#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an6.21"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.21:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.21:0.2"
msgid "3. Anuttariyavagga "
msgstr "3. Unsurpassable "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.21:0.3"
msgid "21. Sāmakasutta "
msgstr "21. At Sāma Village "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.309, sc1
msgctxt "an6.21:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sakkesu viharati sāmagāmake pokkharaṇiyāyaṃ. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying among the Sakyans near the little village of Sāma, by a lotus pond. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.21:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho aññatarā devatā abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇā kevalakappaṃ pokkharaṇiyaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho sā devatā bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then, late at night, a glorious deity, lighting up the entire lotus pond, went up to the Buddha, bowed, stood to one side, and said to him, "

#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an6.21:2.1"
msgid "“Tayome, bhante, dhammā bhikkhuno parihānāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr "“Sir, three qualities lead to the decline of a mendicant. "

msgctxt "an6.21:2.2"
msgid "Katame tayo? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "an6.21:2.3"
msgid "Kammārāmatā, bhassārāmatā, niddārāmatā—"
msgstr "Relishing work, talk, and sleep. "

msgctxt "an6.21:2.4"
msgid "ime kho, bhante, tayo dhammā bhikkhuno parihānāya saṃvattantī”ti. "
msgstr "These three qualities lead to the decline of a mendicant.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.21:2.5"
msgid "Idamavoca sā devatā. "
msgstr "That’s what that deity said, "

msgctxt "an6.21:2.6"
msgid "Samanuñño satthā ahosi. "
msgstr "and the teacher approved. "

msgctxt "an6.21:2.7"
msgid "Atha kho sā devatā “samanuñño me satthā”ti bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā tatthevantaradhāyi. "
msgstr "Then that deity, knowing that the teacher approved, bowed, and respectfully circled the Buddha, keeping him on his right, before vanishing right there. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an6.21:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā tassā rattiyā accayena bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "Then, when the night had passed, the Buddha told the mendicants all that had happened, adding: "

msgctxt "an6.21:3.2"
msgid "“imaṃ, bhikkhave, rattiṃ aññatarā devatā abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇā kevalakappaṃ pokkharaṇiyaṃ obhāsetvā yenāhaṃ tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā maṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho, bhikkhave, sā devatā maṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an6.21:3.3"
msgid "‘tayome, bhante, dhammā bhikkhuno parihānāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an6.21:3.4"
msgid "Katame tayo? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an6.21:3.5"
msgid "Kammārāmatā, bhassārāmatā, niddārāmatā—"
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an6.21:3.6"
msgid "ime kho, bhante, tayo dhammā bhikkhuno parihānāya saṃvattantī’ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.21:3.7"
msgid "Idamavoca, bhikkhave, sā devatā. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an6.21:3.8"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvā maṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā tatthevantaradhāyi. "
msgstr " "

#. VAR: vo → kho (mr)
msgctxt "an6.21:3.9"
msgid "Tesaṃ vo, bhikkhave, alābhā tesaṃ dulladdhaṃ, ye vo devatāpi jānanti kusalehi dhammehi parihāyamāne. "
msgstr "“It’s unfortunate for those of you who even the deities know are declining in skillful qualities. "

#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.310, sc4
msgctxt "an6.21:4.1"
msgid "Aparepi, bhikkhave, tayo parihāniye dhamme desessāmi. "
msgstr "I will teach you three more qualities that lead to decline. "

msgctxt "an6.21:4.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasi karotha, bhāsissāmī”ti. "
msgstr "Listen and pay close attention, I will speak.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.21:4.3"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. "
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” they replied. "

msgctxt "an6.21:4.4"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "The Buddha said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.21:4.5"
msgid "“katame ca, bhikkhave, tayo parihāniyā dhammā? "
msgstr "“And what, mendicants, are three qualities that lead to decline? "

msgctxt "an6.21:4.6"
msgid "Saṅgaṇikārāmatā, dovacassatā, pāpamittatā—"
msgstr "Enjoyment of company, being hard to admonish, and having bad friends. "

msgctxt "an6.21:4.7"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo parihāniyā dhammā. "
msgstr "These three qualities lead to decline. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an6.21:5.1"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ parihāyiṃsu kusalehi dhammehi, sabbete imeheva chahi dhammehi parihāyiṃsu kusalehi dhammehi. "
msgstr "Whether in the past, future, or present, all those who decline in skillful qualities do so because of these six qualities.” "

msgctxt "an6.21:5.2"
msgid "Yepi hi keci, bhikkhave, anāgatamaddhānaṃ parihāyissanti kusalehi dhammehi, sabbete imeheva chahi dhammehi parihāyissanti kusalehi dhammehi. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an6.21:5.3"
msgid "Yepi hi keci, bhikkhave, etarahi parihāyanti kusalehi dhammehi, sabbete imeheva chahi dhammehi parihāyanti kusalehi dhammehī”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.21:5.4"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

